<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>hi, i'm Camille ✦</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300&family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #FDF6EC;
    --blush: #F2C4B2;
    --terracotta: #C96A4A;
    --sage: #7A9E7E;
    --forest: #3B5E42;
    --ink: #1C1C1C;
    --warm-grey: #8A7D74;
    --paper: #FAF3E8;
    --highlight: #F5E642;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background-color: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NOISE TEXTURE OVERLAY ── */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 999;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 20% 80%, #F2C4B240 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 80% 20%, #7A9E7E30 0%, transparent 60%),
      var(--cream);
  }

  .hero-tag {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--terracotta);
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 9rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--warm-grey);
    max-width: 380px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: block;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--warm-grey);
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--warm-grey);
    animation: bob 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes bob {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(6px); }
  }

  /* ── SECTION WRAPPER ── */
  .section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--blush);
  }

  /* ── ABOUT GRID ── */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 1.5rem; }
  }

  .about-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid #E8DDD0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
  }

  .about-card.wide { grid-column: 1 / -1; }

  .card-prompt {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .card-answer {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .card-answer.small {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--blush), transparent);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── STRIPE SECTION ── */
  .stripe {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .stripe .section {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .stripe .section-label {
    color: var(--blush);
  }

  .stripe .section-label::after {
    background: #444;
  }

  /* ── VALUES CHECKLIST ── */
  .values-intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #AAA;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .value-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--sage);
  }

  .value-item.checked {
    border-color: var(--sage);
    background: #7A9E7E18;
  }

  .value-checkbox {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border: 1.5px solid #555;
    border-radius: 5px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }

  .value-item.checked .value-checkbox {
    background: var(--sage);
    border-color: var(--sage);
  }

  .value-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #CCC;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .value-item.checked .value-label {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .match-meter {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .meter-bar-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 150px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #333;
    border-radius: 100px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .meter-bar {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--sage), var(--highlight));
    border-radius: 100px;
    transition: width 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  }

  .meter-text {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #AAA;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .meter-text span {
    color: var(--highlight);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ── FLAGS ── */
  .flags-section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--paper);
  }

  .flags-section .section {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .flags-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .flags-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .flags-column h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .flag-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .flag-item {
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .flag-item.green {
    background: #7A9E7E18;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--sage);
    color: var(--forest);
  }

  .flag-item.red {
    background: #C96A4A15;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--terracotta);
    color: #8B3A20;
  }

  .flag-emoji { flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ── TESTIMONIALS ── */
  .testimonials-section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .testimonials-section .section { padding: 0; }

  .testimonials-intro {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--warm-grey);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .testimonial-scroll {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid #E8DDD0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .testimonial-card::before {
    content: '"';
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 5rem;
    color: var(--blush);
    position: absolute;
    top: -0.5rem;
    left: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1rem;
    background: var(--blush);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .author-role {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--warm-grey);
  }

  /* ── CONTACT FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--cream);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .footer-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blush);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .footer-headline {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .footer-headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--blush);
  }

  .footer-sub {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .footer-link {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .footer-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--blush);
    color: var(--blush);
  }

  .footer-fine {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #555;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── STICKER ACCENTS ── */
  .sticker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    background: var(--highlight);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* ── FADE IN ANIMATION ── */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .fade-up.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ── QUICK FACTS TICKER ── */
  .ticker-wrap {
    background: var(--terracotta);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .ticker {
    display: inline-block;
    animation: ticker 22s linear infinite;
  }

  .ticker span {
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-right: 3rem;
  }

  .ticker span::before {
    content: '✦ ';
    color: var(--highlight);
  }

  @keyframes ticker {
    0% { transform: translateX(0); }
    100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">est. [YEAR] · [CITY]</div>
  <h1 class="hero-name">
    hi, i'm<br><em>[Name].</em>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    [Your one-liner here — something warm, a little funny, totally you. Think: tagline, not biography.]
  </p>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">28</span>
      <span class="stat-label">years old</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">🌇</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Chicago</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">5'7"</span>
      <span class="stat-label">height</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">♋</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Cancer sun</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">↓ scroll to learn more</div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════ TICKER ══════════ -->
<div class="ticker-wrap">
  <div class="ticker">
    <span>dog person</span><span>obsessive playlist curator</span><span>will always split dessert</span><span>bookshelf judger (sorry)</span><span>early riser</span><span>chronic over-tipper</span><span>weekend market person</span><span>asks too many questions</span><span>dog person</span><span>obsessive playlist curator</span><span>will always split dessert</span><span>bookshelf judger (sorry)</span><span>early riser</span><span>chronic over-tipper</span><span>weekend market person</span><span>asks too many questions</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════ ABOUT + PROMPTS ══════════ -->
<section class="section fade-up">
  <div class="section-label">01 — About Me</div>
  <div class="about-grid">

    <div class="about-card wide">
      <div class="card-prompt">The short version</div>
      <p class="card-answer small">
        [2–3 sentences. Paint a picture of your everyday life — what you do, what lights you up, what someone would notice about you in the first 10 minutes. Not a résumé. Think "at a party, not on LinkedIn."]
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="card-prompt">I'll impress you with my ability to —</div>
      <p class="card-answer">[e.g., "remember every album's release year from 2004–2012"]</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="card-prompt">Two truths and a lie —</div>
      <p class="card-answer small">
        1. [Truth]<br>
        2. [Truth]<br>
        3. [Lie — keep 'em guessing]
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="card-prompt">A non-negotiable in my life —</div>
      <p class="card-answer">[e.g., "Sunday morning slow starts. No exceptions."]</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="card-prompt">My love language is —</div>
      <p class="card-answer">[e.g., "Quality time + sending you videos at 11pm that made me think of you"]</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card wide">
      <div class="card-prompt">What I'm actually looking for</div>
      <p class="card-answer small">
        [Be honest here — are you dating casually? Looking for something real? Open to friendship too? This is the place to be direct without being intense. E.g., "Someone I can travel with and also do nothing with. Ideally someone who texts back."]
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ══════════ VALUES CHECKLIST ══════════ -->
<section class="stripe">
  <div class="section fade-up">
    <div class="section-label">02 — Values Check</div>
    <p class="values-intro">
      Check off any values that resonate with you — curious what overlaps we'd have. No wrong answers. No judgment.<br>
      <span style="font-size:0.8rem; opacity:0.5;">(this is just for fun — the meter below updates as you click)</span>
    </p>

    <div class="values-grid" id="valuesGrid">
      <!-- generated by JS -->
    </div>

    <div class="match-meter">
      <div class="meter-bar-wrap">
        <div class="meter-bar" id="meterBar" style="width:0%"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="meter-text">You share <span id="meterNum">0</span> of my values ✦</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════ FLAGS ══════════ -->
<section class="flags-section fade-up">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">03 — Green &amp; Red Flags</div>
    <div class="flags-grid">

      <div class="flags-column">
        <h3>🟢 Green Flags</h3>
        <ul class="flag-list">
          <li class="flag-item green"><span class="flag-emoji">✓</span> Asks follow-up questions when you talk</li>
          <li class="flag-item green"><span class="flag-emoji">✓</span> Has at least one niche, slightly embarrassing passion</li>
          <li class="flag-item green"><span class="flag-emoji">✓</span> Comfortable with silence on long drives</li>
          <li class="flag-item green"><span class="flag-emoji">✓</span> Remembers small things you mentioned weeks ago</li>
          <li class="flag-item green"><span class="flag-emoji">✓</span> Can disagree without making it weird</li>
          <li class="flag-item green"><span class="flag-emoji">✓</span> Reads (anything — magazines count)</li>
          <li class="flag-item green"><span class="flag-emoji">✓</span> Tips well and is kind to service staff</li>
          <li class="flag-item green"><span class="flag-emoji">✓</span> Has a relationship with their family (even a complicated one they've thought about)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="flags-column">
        <h3>🔴 Red Flags</h3>
        <ul class="flag-list">
          <li class="flag-item red"><span class="flag-emoji">✗</span> Makes everything a competition</li>
          <li class="flag-item red"><span class="flag-emoji">✗</span> Talks about exes like case studies in wrongness</li>
          <li class="flag-item red"><span class="flag-emoji">✗</span> "I don't really read" (I'll get over it, but I'll notice)</li>
          <li class="flag-item red"><span class="flag-emoji">✗</span> Chronically non-committal about plans</li>
          <li class="flag-item red"><span class="flag-emoji">✗</span> Performs busyness as a personality trait</li>
          <li class="flag-item red"><span class="flag-emoji">✗</span> Thinks being emotionally unavailable is mysterious</li>
          <li class="flag-item red"><span class="flag-emoji">✗</span> Can't laugh at themselves</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ══════════ TESTIMONIALS ══════════ -->
<section class="testimonials-section fade-up">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">04 — Dispatches from Friends</div>
    <p class="testimonials-intro">
      I asked my people to describe me in one honest paragraph. Here's what they said. (I had no editorial control.)
    </p>

    <div class="testimonial-scroll">

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          [Name] will remember your coffee order after one conversation and somehow also forget to respond to your text for 3 days. It's a paradox. We love them anyway.
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">🌻</div>
          <div>
            <div class="author-name">Jamie R.</div>
            <div class="author-role">friend of 7 years</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          Will absolutely cry at the end of a good book and then recommend it to you immediately. Passionate about everything she cares about. You always know where you stand.
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">🍂</div>
          <div>
            <div class="author-name">Sam K.</div>
            <div class="author-role">college roommate</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

